475
00:22:18,650 --> 00:22:21,060
A-Ako ti pomôžem?

476
00:22:21,060 --> 00:22:22,780
Tak, že my to vysvetlíš.

477
00:22:22,780 --> 00:22:24,720
N-No...

478
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:27,580
Robila som to ako voliteľnú úlohu!

479
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:29,030
Čo to s tebou je?

480
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:30,360
<i>Nie je to priveľké?</i>

481
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,540
A odovzdala.

482
00:22:32,540 --> 00:22:33,720
To vážne?!

483
00:22:33,720 --> 00:22:35,110
